{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_7","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/zsh -lc \"nl -ba gokko-ad-pricing-preview.html | sed -n '430,860p'\"","aggregated_output":"   430\t    .plan-btn { min-width: unset; }\n   431\t    .coeff-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 14px; }\n   432\t    .result-inner { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }\n   433\t    .result-left { justify-content: center; }\n   434\t    .result-total { text-align: center; }\n   435\t    .result-total-value { font-size: 24px; }\n   436\t    .section { padding: 40px 0; }\n   437\t    .section-title { font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 28px; }\n   438\t  }\n   439\t\n   440\t  /* ── Animations ── */\n   441\t  @keyframes fadeUp {\n   442\t    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }\n   443\t    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n   444\t  }\n   445\t  .coeff-card { animation: fadeUp 0.4s ease both; }\n   446\t  .coeff-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.03s; }\n   447\t  .coeff-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.06s; }\n   448\t  .coeff-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.09s; }\n   449\t  .coeff-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.12s; }\n   450\t  .coeff-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }\n   451\t  .coeff-card:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.18s; }\n   452\t\n   453\t  .app-content { display: block; }\n   454\t</style>\n   455\t</head>\n   456\t<body>\n   457\t\n   458\t<!-- ── App Content ── -->\n   459\t<div class=\"app-content\" id=\"appContent\">\n   460\t\n   461\t<!-- ── Hero ── -->\n   462\t<section class=\"hero\">\n   463\t  <div class=\"hero-badge\">GOKKO Inc. — Advertising Menu 2025</div>\n   464\t  <h1>Ad Pricing<br>Simulator</h1>\n   465\t  <p>縦型ショートドラマ広告利用の料金を、プランと各係数からリアルタイムでシミュレーション</p>\n   466\t\n   467\t  <div class=\"plan-selector\" id=\"planSelector\" role=\"radiogroup\" aria-label=\"プラン選択\">\n   468\t    <div class=\"plan-btn\" data-plan=\"0\" role=\"radio\" aria-checked=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">\n   469\t      <span class=\"plan-num\">PLAN 01</span>\n   470\t      <span class=\"plan-name\">ライトプラン</span>\n   471\t      <span class=\"plan-sub\">フック重視</span>\n   472\t    </div>\n   473\t    <div class=\"plan-btn\" data-plan=\"1\" role=\"radio\" aria-checked=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">\n   474\t      <span class=\"plan-num\">PLAN 02</span>\n   475\t      <span class=\"plan-name\">ベーシックプラン</span>\n   476\t      <span class=\"plan-sub\">実稼働費回収</span>\n   477\t    </div>\n   478\t    <div class=\"plan-btn active\" data-plan=\"2\" role=\"radio\" aria-checked=\"true\" tabindex=\"0\">\n   479\t      <span class=\"plan-recommended\">RECOMMENDED</span>\n   480\t      <span class=\"plan-num\">PLAN 03</span>\n   481\t      <span class=\"plan-name\">スタンダードプラン</span>\n   482\t      <span class=\"plan-sub\">バランス型</span>\n   483\t    </div>\n   484\t    <div class=\"plan-btn\" data-plan=\"3\" role=\"radio\" aria-checked=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">\n   485\t      <span class=\"plan-num\">PLAN 04</span>\n   486\t      <span class=\"plan-name\">プレミアムプラン</span>\n   487\t      <span class=\"plan-sub\">アップセル</span>\n   488\t    </div>\n   489\t  </div>\n   490\t</section>\n   491\t\n   492\t<!-- ── Formula Bar ── -->\n   493\t<div class=\"formula-bar\">\n   494\t  <span>総額</span> = 基本出演料 × 使用期間 × 競合排除 × 業界 × メディア × 出演者ランク × マージン\n   495\t</div>\n   496\t\n   497\t<!-- ── Main ── -->\n   498\t<div class=\"container\">\n   499\t\n   500\t  <!-- Base Fee -->\n   501\t  <section class=\"section\">\n   502\t    <div class=\"section-label\">Base Fee</div>\n   503\t    <div class=\"section-title\">基本出演料を入力</div>\n   504\t    <div class=\"base-fee-card\">\n   505\t      <label>ショートドラマ出演時のキャスティング費（税別）</label>\n   506\t      <div class=\"input-row\">\n   507\t        <span>¥</span>\n   508\t        <input type=\"text\" class=\"base-fee-input\" id=\"baseFee\" placeholder=\"100,000\" value=\"100,000\">\n   509\t      </div>\n   510\t    </div>\n   511\t  </section>\n   512\t\n   513\t  <!-- Coefficients -->\n   514\t  <section class=\"section\">\n   515\t    <div class=\"section-label\">Coefficients</div>\n   516\t    <div class=\"section-title\">各係数を選択してください</div>\n   517\t    <div class=\"coeff-grid\" id=\"coeffGrid\"></div>\n   518\t  </section>\n   519\t\n   520\t  <!-- Reference -->\n   521\t  <section class=\"section\">\n   522\t    <div class=\"section-label\">Reference</div>\n   523\t    <div class=\"section-title\">出演者ランク別 基本出演料の目安</div>\n   524\t    <div class=\"ref-table-wrap\">\n   525\t      <table class=\"ref-table\">\n   526\t        <thead>\n   527\t          <tr><th>ランク</th><th>係数</th><th>説明</th><th>基本出演料目安</th></tr>\n   528\t        </thead>\n   529\t        <tbody>\n   530\t          <tr><td>新人A</td><td>×0.8</td><td>GOKKO専属新人</td><td>5万円</td></tr>\n   531\t          <tr><td>新人B</td><td>×1.0</td><td>一般新人キャスト</td><td>8〜12万円</td></tr>\n   532\t          <tr><td>準中堅</td><td>×1.8</td><td>実績ある若手</td><td>15〜25万円</td></tr>\n   533\t          <tr><td>中堅A</td><td>×2.5</td><td>中堅タレント</td><td>30〜40万円</td></tr>\n   534\t          <tr><td>中堅B</td><td>×3.5</td><td>人気中堅タレント</td><td>50〜80万円</td></tr>\n   535\t          <tr><td>準有名</td><td>×5.0</td><td>知名度上昇中</td><td>80〜120万円</td></tr>\n   536\t          <tr><td>有名A</td><td>×8.0</td><td>有名タレント</td><td>150〜300万円</td></tr>\n   537\t          <tr><td>有名S</td><td>×12.0</td><td>トップクラス</td><td>500万円以上</td></tr>\n   538\t        </tbody>\n   539\t      </table>\n   540\t    </div>\n   541\t  </section>\n   542\t</div>\n   543\t\n   544\t<!-- ── Sticky Result ── -->\n   545\t<div class=\"result-panel\" id=\"resultPanel\">\n   546\t  <div class=\"result-inner\">\n   547\t    <div class=\"result-left\">\n   548\t      <div class=\"result-plan-badge\" id=\"resultPlanBadge\">STANDARD</div>\n   549\t      <div class=\"result-breakdown\" id=\"resultBreakdown\"></div>\n   550\t    </div>\n   551\t    <div class=\"result-total\">\n   552\t      <div class=\"result-total-label\">Estimated Total</div>\n   553\t      <div class=\"result-total-value\" id=\"resultValue\">¥0</div>\n   554\t    </div>\n   555\t  </div>\n   556\t</div>\n   557\t\n   558\t<!-- ── Footer ── -->\n   559\t<footer class=\"footer\">\n   560\t  © 2025 GOKKO Inc. All rights reserved. ｜ 本料金表は参考価格です。正式なお見積りは別途ご相談ください。\n   561\t</footer>\n   562\t\n   563\t</div><!-- /app-content -->\n   564\t\n   565\t<script>\n   566\t// ═══════════════════════════════════════\n   567\t// PLAN DATA — 4 plans × 5 coefficient categories\n   568\t// ═══════════════════════════════════════\n   569\tconst PLANS = [\n   570\t  // ── PLAN 0: ライトプラン（フック重視）──\n   571\t  {\n   572\t    name: 'ライトプラン',\n   573\t    nameEn: 'LIGHT',\n   574\t    period: [\n   575\t      { label: '1ヶ月', coeff: 0.8, desc: 'お試し配信' },\n   576\t      { label: '3ヶ月', coeff: 1.0, desc: '短期集中キャンペーン' },\n   577\t      { label: '6ヶ月', coeff: 1.3, desc: '標準的な広告契約' },\n   578\t      { label: '1年',   coeff: 2.0, desc: '年間継続展開' },\n   579\t      { label: '2年',   coeff: 3.0, desc: '長期ブランド戦略' },\n   580\t      { label: '無期限', coeff: 4.0, desc: '恒久的な利用権' },\n   581\t    ],\n   582\t    competition: [\n   583\t      { label: '競合なし',     coeff: 1.0, desc: '基本料金（ドラマと同条件）' },\n   584\t      { label: '商品競合のみ', coeff: 1.3, desc: '同一商品カテゴリを排除' },\n   585\t      { label: '業界競合',     coeff: 1.6, desc: '同一業界全体を排除' },\n   586\t      { label: '全競合排除',   coeff: 2.0, desc: 'すべての競合を排除' },\n   587\t    ],\n   588\t    industry: [\n   589\t      { label: '一般消費財',           coeff: 1.0, desc: '標準的な広告予算規模' },\n   590\t      { label: '食品・飲料',           coeff: 1.1, desc: '頻繁な広告展開が想定' },\n   591\t      { label: '化粧品・美容',         coeff: 1.3, desc: 'イメージ重視で高額予算' },\n   592\t      { label: '金融・保険',           coeff: 1.6, desc: '規制業界で慎重な選定が必要' },\n   593\t      { label: '医療・薬品',           coeff: 1.8, desc: '最高レベルの信頼性が要求' },\n   594\t      { label: 'アルコール・ギャンブル', coeff: 2.0, desc: '特殊な規制対象業界' },\n   595\t    ],\n   596\t    media: [\n   597\t      { label: 'TikTok（基本）',       coeff: 1.0,  desc: '基本配信面', base: true 